<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink390">
<l>nallō rāṅkaṭ parantukai toḻutu</l>
<l>pallūḻ maṟuki viṉavu vōyē</l>
<l>tiṇṭōḷ valviṟ kāḷaiyoṭu</l>
<l>kaṇṭaṉe maṉṟa curattiṭai yāmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Going to [different] places and joining hands [in greeting],  </l>
<l>in distress you ask [the same] many times.  </l>
<l>We have seen her in the desert with a young man, </l>
<l>[who has] strong shoulders and a mighty bow. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
